Title: An Exponential Lower Bound for Depth 3 Arithmetic Circuits  
Author: Dima Grigoriev Marek Karpinski 
Note: Research partially supported by NSF Grant CCR-9424358.  Bonn. Research partially supported by the International Computer Science Institute, Berkeley, DIMACS, by the DFG Grant 673/4-1, ESPRIT BR Grants 7079, 21726, and EC-US 030.  
